6. Risks & Mitigations
*  Risk: Hallucination in Critical Ops. (e.g., delete_file /)
*  Mitigation: Human-in-the-Loop Node. Any destructive tool must transition the graph state to
waiting_for_approval. The agent effectively "pauses" until a human clicks "Approve" in the UI.
*  Risk: Context Window Overflow.
*  Mitigation: Qwen 2.5 supports 32k context comfortably. We will also implement a "Summary Node" in
the graph that compresses conversation history when it exceeds 20k tokens.
