Functional Requirements
*  Deal Intake: Ingest emails/files, classify opportunity, extracting structured metadata (EBITDA,
Revenue).
*  Orchestration: Execute multi-step workflows (e.g., "Triage -> Research -> Draft LOI") with
conditional branching.
*  Human-in-the-Loop: Pause execution for human review on defined triggers (e.g., "Confidence < 70%"
or "Action = Send Email") [B].
